name: 737 GRAVEL RUNWAY LANDING! Air Inuit 737-200 Arrival at Puvirnituq Airport
description:
In August, I had the pleasure of flying on board Air Inuit's Boeing 737-200 from Montreal (YUL) to Puvirnituq (YPX). Puvirnituq has a 6,299' gravel runway, and receives multiple 737 combi flights a week with important cargo for the community.

Enjoy the sights and sounds of this 737-200 landing on a gravel runway!
